## Media Files

**Adding Media:**
1. Run `npm start` and select "Browse media library"
2. Visual browser opens at http://localhost:3001
3. Click any media item to copy its MDX component code
4. Paste directly into this draft

**Media Component Examples:**

Videos (Cloudflare Stream):
<CloudflareVideo videoId="abc123xyz" caption="Body camera footage from the incident" />

Images (Cloudflare Images):
<CloudflareImage imageId="abc123xyz" alt="Scene of the incident" variant="public" />

Documents (Cloudflare R2):
<DocumentLink documentId="complaint-2024-01-15" title="Civil Rights Complaint" description="Original complaint filed by the victim" />

